<%= render "marketing_nav" %>

<section class="relative overflow-hidden landing-hero-drench pt-24 pb-20" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="landing-hero-pattern"></div>
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-1"></div>
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-2"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pt-16">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-[#b8d4b5] uppercase mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">For Compliance Officers</p>
        <h1 class="landing-hero-title text-balance text-5xl leading-none sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
          Audit trail built into<br>
          <span class="landing-hero-accent">every transaction.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="landing-hero-body mt-6 max-w-xl text-balance text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Every action logged. Every document archived. Every report traceable to the source.
          Sirib captures the audit trail automatically — so when the regulator calls,
          you're ready. Not scrambling through filing cabinets.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <a href="#demo" class="landing-hero-cta landing-hero-cta-primary">See It in Action</a>
          <a href="/session/new" class="landing-hero-cta landing-hero-cta-outline">Try a Demo</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden lg:block">
        <div class="landing-browser-frame">
          <div class="landing-browser-toolbar">
            <span class="landing-browser-dot" style="background:#ff5f57"></span>
            <span class="landing-browser-dot" style="background:#ffbd2e"></span>
            <span class="landing-browser-dot" style="background:#28c840"></span>
          </div>
          <img src="<%= image_path('screenshots/dashboard.svg') %>" alt="Compliance dashboard in Sirib">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-[#f0f7ef] border-b border-[#e7e5e4] py-12" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="landing-stats-value">100%</p>
        <p class="landing-stats-label">transaction traceability</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="landing-stats-value">30+</p>
        <p class="landing-stats-label">regulatory reports auto-generated</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="landing-stats-value">15 min</p>
        <p class="landing-stats-label">audit prep time</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-b border-[#e7e5e4] py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-3" style="top: -5rem; right: 15%; opacity: 0.6;"></div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-[#5b8c5a] uppercase mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">The Flow</p>
      <h2 class="text-balance text-3xl font-normal tracking-[-0.03em] text-[#1c1917] sm:text-4xl">
        How compliance works in Sirib from transaction to report
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-4" data-reveal-item>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2"/><rect x="9" y="3" width="6" height="4" rx="1"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 1</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Transaction occurs</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Deposit, withdrawal, loan disbursement, journal entry — any action. Sirib captures who did it, when, with what approval, and on what account.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M7 12h10M7 12a2 2 0 1 0 0 4h10a2 2 0 1 0 0-4M7 12v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 2</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Audit log created</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Immutable record written: timestamp, user, action type, before/after values, IP address. Append-only — no editing, no deleting.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 7a2 2 0 1 1 4 0v4a2 2 0 0 1-4 0V7z"/><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0 9 9 0 0 0-18 0"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 3</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Compliance check</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">System checks thresholds, limits, regulatory requirements. Flags anything that needs attention or documentation — before it becomes a finding.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0 9 9 0 0 0-18 0"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 4</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Document archived</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">All supporting documents attached and archived to the transaction automatically. Retrievable in one search — no digging through filing cabinets.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-b border-[#e7e5e4] py-24 bg-[#faf9f7]" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-[#5b8c5a] uppercase mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">What Gets Automated</p>
      <h2 class="text-balance text-3xl font-normal tracking-[-0.03em] text-[#1c1917] sm:text-4xl">
        The tasks Sirib handles so you're always audit-ready
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4" data-reveal-item>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2"/><rect x="9" y="3" width="6" height="4" rx="1"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Real-time audit trail</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Every action logged automatically — who, what, when, before/after. Immutable, append-only, never editable. Auditors can trace any transaction end to end.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M15 12h3M15 12a2 2 0 1 0 0 4h3"/><path d="M4 12h7m0 0-2-2m2 2-2 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Threshold monitoring</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Single transaction limits, aggregate daily exposures, and unusual activity flagged in real time. Compliance officer reviews exceptions, not every transaction.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="M18 9l-5 5-4-4-3 3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Regulatory reports</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">BSP, CDA, and cooperative development reports generated from live data. No manual compilation. Format-ready for submission with a single export.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 6V2M6 12H2M12 22v-4M22 12h-4M15.07 4.93l-2.11 2.11M8.93 15.07l-2.11 2.11M15.07 15.07l2.11 2.11M4.93 8.93L7.04 6.82"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Document retention</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Regulatory retention schedules applied automatically. Documents tagged, aged, and retained per policy. Auditors can access the complete history — not what survived a filing cabinet.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

